title.Value: Team Penning in Kalispell, Montana by MontanaPictures.Net

description.Name: description
description.Value:
Team Penning" competition at the Northwest Montana Fair in Kalispell, Montana. Team Penning = Three riders get sixty seconds to select three yearling calves from a herd and move them to a 16' x 24' holding pen on the opposite side of the arena.
Visit over 250 Montana towns at http://www.MontanaPictures.Net "The website for people homesick for Montana.
